  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,36,"Experience shared with the permission of Frank Blair. Brother Blair, now 89 years old, was present in the Conference Center for this address."
  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,37,"The Hebrew word translated “repent” in, for example,Ezekiel 14:6isshoob(transliterated). It means “to turn back” or “return.” (See James Strong,The Exhaustive Concordance of the Bible[1890], no. 7725.)"
  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,38,"SeeJacob 6:5;Mosiah 16:12;Alma 5:33;19:36;29:10;3 Nephi 9:14."
  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,39,"Doctrine and Covenants 58:26."
  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,40,"Doctrine and Covenants 58:25; emphasis added."
  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/take-the-holy-spirit-as-your-guide,Elder Larry Y. Wilson,41,"Alma 37:37; emphasis added."
