  2018,"04",/general-conference/2018/04/what-every-aaronic-priesthood-holder-needs-to-understand,Douglas D. Holmes,46,"See James Strong,The New Strong’s Exhaustive Concordance of the Bible(1984), Hebrew and Chaldee dictionary section, 66, Greek dictionary section, 7."
